WEBVTT

00:01.042 --> 00:02.419
AH-HYUCK.

00:02.419 --> 00:04.629
♪ H-H-H-HIT IT ♪

00:04.629 --> 00:06.798
♪ LIKE FATHER, LIKE SON ♪

00:06.798 --> 00:09.175
♪ YOU'RE ALWAYS NUMBER ONE ♪
YES!

00:09.175 --> 00:12.095
♪ BEST BUDDIES, BEST PALS ♪
♪ YEAH ♪

00:12.095 --> 00:14.097
♪ YOU ALWAYS SEEM
TO WORK THINGS OUT ♪

00:14.097 --> 00:16.391
♪ CAN'T YOU SEE
YOU'RE TWO OF A KIND ♪

00:16.391 --> 00:18.810
♪ LOOKIN' FOR
A REAL GOOD TIME? ♪

00:18.810 --> 00:20.437
WHAA-OOO-HO-HO!

00:20.437 --> 00:22.105
♪ A REAL GOOD TIME ♪

00:22.105 --> 00:24.107
♪ REPORT
TO THE GOOF TROOP ♪

00:24.107 --> 00:25.775
♪ AND WE'LL ALWAYS
STICK TOGETHER ♪

00:25.775 --> 00:27.777
♪ ALWAYS
STICK TOGETHER ♪

00:27.777 --> 00:29.404
♪ WE'RE THE GOOF TROOP ♪

00:29.404 --> 00:31.656
♪ THE BEST OF FRIENDS
FOREVER ♪

00:33.116 --> 00:35.243
♪ SIDE BY SIDE
WHEREVER WE GO ♪

00:35.243 --> 00:39.622
♪ WE'RE ALWAYS READY TO ROLL ♪

00:39.622 --> 00:41.249
♪ NOW GIMME A BEAT ♪

00:41.249 --> 00:42.584
♪ WE'RE THE GOOF TROOP ♪

00:42.584 --> 00:45.587
♪ AND WE ALWAYS
STICK TOGETHER ♪

00:45.587 --> 00:47.589
GAWRSH.
♪ WE'RE THE GOOF TROOP ♪

00:47.589 --> 00:51.468
♪ THE BEST OF FRIENDS
FOREVER ♪

00:51.468 --> 00:53.845
♪ NOW WE'RE CALLING
EVERYONE ♪

00:53.845 --> 00:55.680
♪ COME ALONG
AND JOIN THE FUN ♪

00:55.680 --> 00:57.432
♪ REPORT TO
THE GOOF TROOP ♪

00:57.432 --> 00:58.767
♪ LA DO BE DA BOP
LA BA DO BOP ♪

00:58.767 --> 00:59.851
YEAH!

01:01.603 --> 01:05.148
PJ: AXED BY ADDITION!
SLAIN BY SUBTRACTION!

01:05.148 --> 01:06.608
(SIGHS)

01:06.608 --> 01:08.985
EVERY TIME I SEE A NUMBER,
I FREAK OUT!

01:08.985 --> 01:12.197
I'M GOING TO FLUNK
MY MATH FINAL FOR SURE!

01:12.197 --> 01:13.656
(KNOCKING ON DOOR)

01:15.200 --> 01:18.578
SO, HOW'S DADDY'S LITTLE
EINSTEIN?

01:18.578 --> 01:19.788
(STAMMERING) UH...

01:19.788 --> 01:22.082
FINE, DAD!
RELATIVELY SPEAKING.

01:22.082 --> 01:23.750
HA-HA! IT'S A JOKE.

01:23.750 --> 01:26.252
JUST TRYING TO GET THIS
MATH THING THROUGH MY HEAD.

01:26.252 --> 01:29.255
WHY, YOUR HEAD CAN DO
ANYTHING YOU PUT IT TO.

01:29.255 --> 01:31.424
YOU GOT MY BRAINS IN IT!

01:31.424 --> 01:34.177
WHAT SAY DADDY
GIVES YOU A LITTLE POP QUIZ?

01:34.177 --> 01:36.638
WHOA!

01:36.638 --> 01:38.682
NOW, WHAT'S FIVE TIMES 12
TO THE TENTH POWER

01:38.682 --> 01:40.475
DIVIDED BY EIGHT MINUS
THE SQUARE ROOT OF SIX?

01:40.475 --> 01:41.810
- WELL, UM...
- AND WHILE YOU'RE AT IT,

01:41.810 --> 01:43.478
HOW MANY FEATHERS
DOES A MONGOOSE HAVE?

01:43.478 --> 01:45.146
AND WHAT WAS THE NAME
OF THE UNKNOWN SOLDIER?

01:45.146 --> 01:46.564
AND HOW MUCH WOOD
WOULD A WOODCHUCK CHUCK,

01:46.564 --> 01:47.649
IF A WOODCHUCK
COULD CHUCK WOOD?

01:47.649 --> 01:49.693
I CAN'T EVEN SAY THAT!

01:49.693 --> 01:52.070
HA! YOU THINK THAT'S HARD?

01:52.070 --> 01:53.905
YOU KIDS HAVE IT EASY.

01:53.905 --> 01:58.326
WHY, WHEN I WAS YOUR AGE
I FOUGHT FOR AN EDUCATION!

01:58.326 --> 02:00.829
HAD TO TRUDGE 20 MILES
THROUGH THE SNOW

02:00.829 --> 02:02.539
AND DEFROST MY PENCIL
TO TAKE A TEST!

02:02.539 --> 02:04.833
WOULD'VE GOT MY PH. AND MY D,

02:04.833 --> 02:09.337
IF I HADN'T EXCEEDED THE STATUTE
OF LIMITATIONS ON HIGH SCHOOL.

02:09.337 --> 02:11.297
BUT NOW I'VE GOT A SON

02:11.297 --> 02:14.926
TO PICK UP WHERE I
DROPPED A GRADE POINT.

02:14.926 --> 02:16.720
AHH, YEAH, UM...

02:16.720 --> 02:21.224
BUT WHAT IF--
THIS IS JUST IF--I FLUNK?

02:21.224 --> 02:22.350
FLUNK?

02:22.350 --> 02:25.562
AND MAKE MY BRAINS LOOK BAD?

02:25.562 --> 02:27.605
IT'S A SIMPLE EQUATION!

02:27.605 --> 02:28.940
YOU'RE GONNA PASS THAT TEST

02:28.940 --> 02:30.900
IF YOU HAVE TO STUDY
ALL NIGHT, SEE?

02:30.900 --> 02:34.946
FLUNK AND YOU'RE GROUNDED
FOREVER!

02:36.865 --> 02:37.949
(DOOR SLAMS)

02:41.703 --> 02:43.413
(WHIMPERING)

02:43.413 --> 02:46.791
MAX! MAX, YOU'VE GOT TO HELP ME!

02:46.791 --> 02:48.209
MAX!

02:52.422 --> 02:54.674
NUMBERS FREAK YOU OUT,
HUH, BUD?

02:54.674 --> 02:57.135
WELL,
YOU'RE NOT THE FIRST GUY

02:57.135 --> 02:59.471
I SAVED FROM
AN INVERTED FRACTION.

02:59.471 --> 03:03.558
NOW, I COULD HELP YOU
CHEAT ON THE TEST...

03:03.558 --> 03:08.063
OR I COULD MAKE YOU
A MATH GENIUS FOR LIFE!

03:11.483 --> 03:13.568
BRAINS OVER CON.

03:13.568 --> 03:14.986
BRAINS IT IS.

03:14.986 --> 03:17.322
WE'LL START
WITH THE EASY STUFF.

03:17.322 --> 03:18.990
WHAT'S 2 PLUS 2?

03:18.990 --> 03:20.825
OKAY, I KNOW THAT ONE.
UH, 2 PLUS 2...

03:20.825 --> 03:22.744
UM, 2 PLUS 2 IS, UM, 4,

03:22.744 --> 03:25.121
AND 4'S 8,
AND CARRY THE 2--
UH, JUST A MINUTE.

03:25.121 --> 03:26.539
16 AND 2'S 18!

03:26.539 --> 03:28.416
NO, NO, DIVIDE
BY 4, IS UM...

03:28.416 --> 03:30.001
(SIGHS)

03:30.001 --> 03:31.294
NO WAIT, WAIT!
DON'T TELL ME, MAN.

03:31.294 --> 03:33.046
IT'S ON THE TIP
OF MY TOENAIL!

03:33.046 --> 03:34.214
UM, LET'S SEE...

03:34.214 --> 03:36.716
5 TIMES 448 MILLION,
AH, IT'S...

03:36.716 --> 03:38.468
UM, UM...

03:38.468 --> 03:40.970
I THINK THIS IS GOING
TO TAKE DRASTIC MEASURES.

03:40.970 --> 03:42.597
OH, DRASTIC IS GOOD!
I LOVE DRASTIC.

03:42.597 --> 03:45.850
I'LL DO ANYTHING TO PASS
THIS TEST! ANYTHING!

03:45.850 --> 03:48.812
UH, CAN I RETHINK THAT?

03:48.812 --> 03:51.981
HEY, TRUST ME,
PEEJANO, MY MAN.

03:51.981 --> 03:53.441
WHEN I'M THROUGH,

03:53.441 --> 03:56.027
YOU'LL MAKE EINSTEIN
LOOK LIKE HOWDY DOODY.

03:56.027 --> 03:58.988
ANSWER RIGHT AND YOU GET THIS!

04:01.491 --> 04:04.869
A FUDGY WUDGY BAR.
MMM, YOUR FAVE!

04:04.869 --> 04:06.913
BUT ANSWER WRONG,
AND THE YOKE'S ON YOU!

04:06.913 --> 04:08.123
(BUZZER BLARING)

04:09.124 --> 04:11.209
- ARE YOU READY?
- UH-UH!

04:11.209 --> 04:12.502
WHAT'S THE SQUARE ROOT OF 9!

04:12.502 --> 04:13.795
UH, ROOTS AREN'T SQUARE, MAN.

04:13.795 --> 04:15.588
THEY'RE LONG AND STRINGY AND--
3!

04:15.588 --> 04:17.298
FARMER NEEDS 400 POUNDS
OF NAILS TO BUILD A BARN.

04:17.298 --> 04:18.633
HOW MANY APPLES WILL IT HOLD?

04:18.633 --> 04:19.968
WHAT DO APPLES HAVE TO DO
WITH--

04:19.968 --> 04:21.177
- (BUZZER BLARING)
- HIS WHOLE CROP!

04:21.177 --> 04:22.512
WHAT'S THE LOGARITHM OF 12?

04:22.512 --> 04:23.847
THE CIRCUMFERENCE OF A CIRCLE?

04:23.847 --> 04:24.973
HOW MANY CHICKENS DOES IT TAKE

04:24.973 --> 04:26.474
TO CROSS THE ROAD?

04:26.474 --> 04:28.393
WHAT KIND OF ANGLES
DOES A SQUARE ROOT HAVE?

04:28.393 --> 04:30.020
RIGHT. JUST GIVE ME
A MINUTE. I, I--

04:30.020 --> 04:31.521
RIGHT ANGLES IS CORRECT!

04:33.523 --> 04:34.566
WHAT'S 2 PLUS 2?

04:34.566 --> 04:35.525
UH, 4?

04:35.525 --> 04:37.152
- 4 PLUS 4?
- 8.

04:37.152 --> 04:38.695
- 8 PLUS 8?
- 14.

04:38.695 --> 04:40.655
- (BUZZER BLARING)
- 16!

04:40.655 --> 04:43.658
MAX, NO MORE!
I'M GOING TO BE SICK!

04:43.658 --> 04:45.160
YOU'RE GOING TO BE BRILLIANT!

04:45.160 --> 04:46.661
BUT ANSWER WRONG
AND THE YOKE'S ON YOU!

04:46.661 --> 04:48.038
(ECHOING) THE YOKE'S ON YOU!

04:48.038 --> 04:49.164
THE YOKE'S ON YOU,

04:49.164 --> 04:51.041
THE YOKE'S ON YOU...

04:56.588 --> 04:58.673
COME ON, PJ! THE BUS IS HERE!

05:00.592 --> 05:02.260
Pete: TOAST, SON?

05:02.260 --> 05:04.012
TWO SLICES OR THREE?

05:04.012 --> 05:07.098
2 PLUS 3 IS 5!
MINUS 2 IS 3!
MINUS 2 IS 1!

05:07.098 --> 05:08.850
OKAY, SO YOU CAN ADD!

05:08.850 --> 05:10.518
WANT AN EGG?

05:10.518 --> 05:11.728
(SCREAMS)

05:11.728 --> 05:14.564
OKAY, NO EGGS!

05:14.564 --> 05:18.735
SAY, DON'T TELL ME YOU WANT
A CANDY BAR FOR BREAKFAST?

05:18.735 --> 05:19.903
(SCREAMS)

05:20.945 --> 05:22.530
DOWN, PJ, DOWN!

05:24.783 --> 05:28.203
(BABBLING)

05:28.203 --> 05:30.914
AND TOAST AND JELLY AND
ON THE SIDE A PIECE OF...

05:36.878 --> 05:39.881
SAY, WHAT'S WRONG WITH HIM?

05:39.881 --> 05:42.467
HE MEMORIZED THE MATH
BOOK 47 TIMES.

05:42.467 --> 05:44.552
I THINK HE'S GOT
NUMBERS ON THE BRAIN.

05:44.552 --> 05:45.887
HUH?

05:45.887 --> 05:49.057
OH, PLAYING SICK, EH?

05:49.057 --> 05:51.309
TRYIN' TO GET
OUT OF THAT TEST, EH?

05:51.309 --> 05:52.769
WELL, YOU CAN'T FOOL ME, SEE?

05:52.769 --> 05:55.105
I WAS A FOOL WAY
BEFORE YOU WERE BORN!

05:55.105 --> 05:57.399
I DON'T CARE IF YOU'VE GOT
BLISTERS ON THE BRAIN

05:57.399 --> 05:58.650
OR WATER ON THE KNEE!

05:58.650 --> 06:01.277
YOU'RE NOT MISSING
THAT TEST!

06:01.277 --> 06:03.738
NOW GO OUT THERE
AND UPHOLD THE FAMILY IQ!

06:07.492 --> 06:09.786
(CHATTER)

06:09.786 --> 06:13.289
OKAY, PEEJ, NOW CRANK UP
THOSE BRAIN CELLS!

06:13.289 --> 06:15.834
YOU'RE GOING TO ACE
THIS BABY, I KNOW IT.

06:15.834 --> 06:18.586
2 PLUS 2 IS 4,
TIMES 8 IS 32,

06:18.586 --> 06:22.799
TIMES 4 IS 38,
MINUS 2 IS 36,
PLUS 5 IS 30...

06:22.799 --> 06:25.218
Max: CIRCUMFERENCE
OF A CIRCLE!

06:25.218 --> 06:27.137
LOGARITHM OF 12!

06:27.137 --> 06:29.931
40 AND 6 TO THE 23rd POWER!

06:29.931 --> 06:31.850
ANSWER WRONG AND
THE YOKE'S ON YOU,

06:31.850 --> 06:35.437
YOU, THE YOKE'S ON YOU!

06:39.816 --> 06:40.942
(BELL RINGS)

06:40.942 --> 06:42.652
SO, EINSTEIN JR.,

06:42.652 --> 06:45.030
HOW DOES IT FEEL
TO ACE A TEST?

06:45.030 --> 06:47.866
I DON'T KNOW.
IT'S ALL A BLANK.

06:47.866 --> 06:49.951
BUT YOU MEMORIZED THE BOOK!

06:49.951 --> 06:53.663
YOU HAVE TO HAVE GOTTEN 'EM
MOSTLY RIGHT, RIGHT?

06:53.663 --> 06:55.623
HALF RIGHT?

06:55.623 --> 06:57.959
PJ, A QUARTER RIGHT?

06:57.959 --> 07:00.628
ALL I REMEMBER IS
FLYING EGGS AND STUFF!

07:00.628 --> 07:03.965
MAX! WHAT IF I FLUNKED?

07:03.965 --> 07:05.633
FLUNKED? OH, NO!

07:05.633 --> 07:07.344
WHEN YOUR DAD FINDS OUT,
YOU'RE GONNA BE...

07:07.344 --> 07:09.471
GROUNDED FOR LIFE!

07:09.471 --> 07:12.515
OH, MAN, DAD WILL GET
MY REPORT CARD

07:12.515 --> 07:14.809
TOMORROW IN THE 3:30 MAIL!

07:14.809 --> 07:19.022
ONLY 23 HOURS
AND 14 MINUTES LEFT TO GO!

07:19.022 --> 07:24.152
IT'S LIKE, AWFUL KNOWING
WHEN YOUR LIFE'S GONNA END.

07:24.152 --> 07:26.988
AW, PEEJ.

07:26.988 --> 07:29.532
WAIT A MINUTE.
IT'S NOT OVER YET!

07:29.532 --> 07:32.160
YOU GOT 23 HOURS
AND 14 MINUTES

07:32.160 --> 07:35.914
TO DO EVERYTHING YOU EVER WANTED
TO DO IN YOUR WHOLE LIFE!

07:35.914 --> 07:38.958
EVEN THE STUFF
I'D GET KILLED FOR?

07:38.958 --> 07:42.379
WHAT'VE YOU GOT TO LOSE?
PJ, YOU'RE DEAD MEAT ANYWAY.

07:47.676 --> 07:50.303
OKAY, I WANNA EAT
200 GORILLA BURGERS.

07:50.303 --> 07:52.555
- CHECK.
- WATCH ALL 12 MUTILATOR MOVIES.

07:52.555 --> 07:54.015
- GOT IT.
- OH,

07:54.015 --> 07:55.392
RIDE DOWN HAIRPIN HILL
IN A SHOPPING CART.

07:55.392 --> 07:56.685
A MUST.

07:56.685 --> 07:58.353
GOTTA KISS CYNTHIA SNODFREW.

07:58.353 --> 07:59.938
YEAH! OLD PERSIMMON LIPS!

07:59.938 --> 08:04.192
OH! AND GO ON THE THREE
WORST RIDES AT TERRORLAND!

08:04.192 --> 08:07.696
WHOA! WELL,
IT IS YOUR FUNERAL.

08:07.696 --> 08:09.072
OKAY LET'S MOVE IT.

08:09.072 --> 08:10.573
YOUR REPORT CARD
COMES AT 3:30.

08:10.573 --> 08:13.702
OH, MAN, WHAT ARE WE
TALKING ABOUT?

08:13.702 --> 08:15.412
WE GOT TO GO TO SCHOOL!

08:15.412 --> 08:17.914
NOT IF WE'RE SICK WE DON'T!

08:17.914 --> 08:21.376
SICK? COME ON, MY DAD
DOESN'T LET ME STAY HOME

08:21.376 --> 08:22.919
UNLESS I'M A WALKING CORPSE!

08:22.919 --> 08:25.714
YOUR WISH IS MY COMMAND.

08:27.507 --> 08:30.885
SO, UH, WHAT LOOKS
GOOD TODAY?

08:30.885 --> 08:35.390
OUTER MONGOLIAN WORRY WARTS
OR PERUVIAN PUS FACE?

08:35.390 --> 08:37.559
AH, WE'LL MIX 'EM
AND MATCH 'EM.

08:37.559 --> 08:39.060
THE GROSSER THE BETTER.

08:40.228 --> 08:41.896
- WELL, I DON'T--
- (SPLATTER)

08:41.896 --> 08:43.398
YUCK!

08:43.398 --> 08:45.734
EVEN IF YOUR DAD DOES
SEND YOU TO SCHOOL,

08:45.734 --> 08:48.570
NO WAY THEY'D LET YOU IN.

08:48.570 --> 08:50.989
I ALWAYS KNEW BROCCOLI
WAS GOOD FOR SOMETHING.

08:54.617 --> 08:57.328
MAN, YOU OUGHTA BE
HANGING IN A GALLERY.

08:57.328 --> 09:00.040
YOU'RE A WORK OF ART!
(SMACKING LIPS)

09:00.040 --> 09:02.459
- (ALARM CLOCK RINGING)
- Pete: (GROANING) PJ?

09:02.459 --> 09:04.627
(YAWNING)
RISE AND SHINE!

09:04.627 --> 09:06.171
IT'S SHOW TIME!

09:11.509 --> 09:13.470
Pete: COME ON, UP AND AT 'EM!

09:14.929 --> 09:17.432
DAD, I DON'T FEEL SO GOOD.

09:18.641 --> 09:20.477
CAN I STAY HOME?

09:21.478 --> 09:22.479
(SCREAMING)

09:25.940 --> 09:27.650
(STAMMERING)

09:27.650 --> 09:29.527
YOU'RE DISINTEGRATING!

09:30.695 --> 09:32.447
QUICK! EMERGENCY!

09:32.447 --> 09:34.449
GET HIM...
(SHOUTING GIBBERISH)

09:34.449 --> 09:36.368
DAD, IT'S REALLY
NOT THAT BAD.

09:36.368 --> 09:38.787
GIMME A SIREN!
I MEAN, AN AMBULANCE!

09:38.787 --> 09:40.830
MY KID'S SICK WITH THE CRUD!

09:45.085 --> 09:46.127
- (SIREN BLARING)
- HUH?

09:50.465 --> 09:53.802
OKAY, PJ! THE COAST IS CLEAR!

09:53.802 --> 09:54.803
HUH?

10:00.558 --> 10:04.688
CAREFUL! EASY!
HE MIGHT FALL APART ANY MINUTE!

10:04.688 --> 10:06.356
OH, NO!

10:06.356 --> 10:08.191
HELP!

10:08.191 --> 10:10.860
AW, DON'T WORRY, SON.

10:10.860 --> 10:13.738
DADDY WILL GET YOU
SPACKLED BACK TOGETHER!

10:16.324 --> 10:17.575
(GROANING)

10:22.205 --> 10:24.791
COME ON! OUTER MONGOLIAN
WORRY WARTS

10:24.791 --> 10:26.543
AND PERUVIAN PUS FACE!

10:26.543 --> 10:29.129
AND THIS KID'S GOT 'EM BOTH!

10:29.129 --> 10:32.132
CALLING DR. CHASM.
REPORT TO SURGERY PLEASE.

10:32.132 --> 10:34.426
DR. CHASM, REPORT TO SURGERY.

10:39.514 --> 10:41.725
(SOBBING)

10:41.725 --> 10:43.852
THE POOR LITTLE KID!

10:43.852 --> 10:46.563
IT'S ALL MY FAULT!

10:46.563 --> 10:49.733
I MADE HIM STAY UP ALL NIGHT
STUDYING.

10:49.733 --> 10:51.026
(SNIFFLING)

10:53.737 --> 10:55.363
USED TO YELL AT HIM

10:55.363 --> 10:59.034
FOR SQUEEZING HIS TOOTHYPASTE
FROM THE WRONG END.

10:59.034 --> 11:02.370
MADE HIM JOIN
GUM POPPERS ANONYMOUS

11:02.370 --> 11:05.790
AND KISS HIS LITTLE
SISTER IN PUBLIC.

11:06.916 --> 11:08.501
AND BRUSH THE DOG'S TEETH

11:08.501 --> 11:10.837
AND USE A MANLY DEODORANT

11:10.837 --> 11:13.840
AND WASH HIS SHOES
BEFORE HE CAME IN THE HOUSE!

11:13.840 --> 11:16.885
I EVEN MADE HIM
USE A HANDKERCHIEF!

11:16.885 --> 11:19.012
(SOBBING)

11:19.012 --> 11:21.931
DELIVERY FOR ROOM 202.
SIGN HERE, PLEASE.

11:21.931 --> 11:24.059
HMM, SECOND ONE TODAY.

11:27.562 --> 11:30.273
OKAY, WELL, WE'LL NEED
A FULL BLOOD PANEL,

11:30.273 --> 11:32.984
A BELLY BUTTON SCAN,
AND A COMPLETE
NOSE HAIR ANALYSIS.

11:32.984 --> 11:34.819
WAIT! UH, I'M AWFULLY WEAK.

11:34.819 --> 11:36.154
CAN I COME BACK
NEXT YEAR, PLEASE?

11:36.154 --> 11:37.781
DON'T WORRY.
NOTHING TO IT.

11:37.781 --> 11:39.407
(ELECTRICITY CRACKLING)

11:39.407 --> 11:41.326
NO! WAIT! OKAY, OKAY,
I'M GONNA TELL YOU SOMETHING!

11:41.326 --> 11:43.995
BUT ONLY IF YOU PROMISE
NOT TO TELL MY DAD!

11:43.995 --> 11:45.955
Max: (OVER P.A.)
CALLING DR. HOWARD,

11:45.955 --> 11:48.041
DR. FINE, DR. HOWARD,

11:48.041 --> 11:50.251
REPORT TO SURGERY, PLEASE.

11:53.505 --> 11:56.341
NO! NO! DON'T OPERATE!
OKAY! OKAY! I GIVE! I GIVE!

11:56.341 --> 11:59.260
I'M NOT REALLY SICK!

11:59.260 --> 12:02.806
OH, YES, YOU ARE!

12:02.806 --> 12:07.811
GANGWAY! GOT AN EMERGENCY HERE!
CODE PURPLE! HEADS UP!

12:07.811 --> 12:08.937
- CLEAR THE ROAD!
- (PEOPLE SHOUTING)

12:08.937 --> 12:09.979
WHOA!

12:12.857 --> 12:14.651
AND THEN ONE TIME,

12:14.651 --> 12:17.028
I MADE HIM PLUCK THE DOG
HAIRS OUT OF THE CARPET

12:17.028 --> 12:18.488
WITH TWEEZERS

12:18.488 --> 12:20.115
AND SENT HIM
TO OBEDIENCE SCHOOL

12:20.115 --> 12:21.991
WHEN HE WOULDN'T
CLEAN UP HIS ROOM.

12:21.991 --> 12:24.452
(SOBBING)

12:24.452 --> 12:26.955
I JUST WANT HIM
TO FORGIVE ME,

12:26.955 --> 12:30.583
AND IF THAT AIN'T THE TRUTH,
MAY I GET STRUCK BY A--

12:34.963 --> 12:36.381
WHAT THE...

12:36.381 --> 12:40.677
SO HE TRIED TO PULL THE
BROCCOLI OVER OUR EYES!

12:40.677 --> 12:43.346
MR. PETE? YOUR SON IS GONE.

12:43.346 --> 12:45.181
(SCREAMING)

12:45.181 --> 12:48.143
HE MELTED AWAY!

12:48.143 --> 12:51.855
GONE TO THAT GREAT BIG
PLAYGROUND IN THE SKY!

12:51.855 --> 12:55.025
NO, HE TOOK OFF! SPLIT!
VAMOOSED!

12:55.025 --> 12:56.818
BUT HE LEFT THIS!

12:57.986 --> 12:59.237
HUH?

12:59.237 --> 13:01.990
"STUFF I WANNA DO
ON MY LAST DAY."

13:01.990 --> 13:04.909
(WAILING) WHAT A KID!

13:04.909 --> 13:06.411
(BLUBBERING)

13:06.411 --> 13:07.996
GOING OUT WITH A BANG,

13:07.996 --> 13:10.832
JUST LIKE I WOULD'VE DONE!

13:10.832 --> 13:12.917
I GOTTA GET HIM TO FORGIVE ME

13:12.917 --> 13:17.839
WHILE THERE'S STILL
SOMETHING LEFT!

13:17.839 --> 13:20.633
NO! NO! NO!
YOU DON'T UNDERSTAND!

13:23.136 --> 13:25.847
C'MON, PEEJ! ONLY THREE
HOURS 41 MINUTES LEFT!

13:25.847 --> 13:27.682
WHA... WHO... HUH...

13:27.682 --> 13:30.685
PJ!

13:30.685 --> 13:34.731
HOLD TOGETHER, SON!
PAPA'S COMIN'!

13:38.568 --> 13:40.403
THREE HOURS,
30 MINUTES TO GO!

13:40.403 --> 13:42.447
WE'VE GOTTA MOVE
AT WARP SPEED, DUDE!

13:50.872 --> 13:54.042
OH, NO! I LOST MY LIST!

13:54.042 --> 13:56.294
NO PROBLEMA.
I KNOW IT BY HEART!

13:56.294 --> 13:59.756
FIRST UP, 200 GORILLA BURGERS!

13:59.756 --> 14:02.842
Man: YOU WANNA BE COOL
WITH YOUR MOUTH FULL?

14:02.842 --> 14:05.637
HUNKY MONKEY FANS,
CHEW ON THIS!

14:05.637 --> 14:07.889
THE GORILLA BURGER!
TWO POUNDS

14:07.889 --> 14:10.809
OF TONGUE-TANTALIZING
MYSTERY MEAT!

14:10.809 --> 14:14.437
EAT QUICK, PAL! STILL GOTTA
SEE ALL 12 MUTILATOR MOVIES!

14:14.437 --> 14:15.814
(GOBBLING)

14:15.814 --> 14:18.274
Pete: TWO HUNDRED BURGERS?

14:18.274 --> 14:20.276
MUST'VE BEEN ALL THOSE TIMES

14:20.276 --> 14:22.570
I SENT HIM TO BED
WITHOUT SECONDS!

14:26.324 --> 14:29.327
PJ, I'M SORRY!

14:34.666 --> 14:36.543
PJ!

14:40.880 --> 14:42.424
HOLD IT, BUB!

14:42.424 --> 14:44.801
I'M GIVING YOU A TICKET
FOR JAY-DRIVING!

14:44.801 --> 14:46.469
NO, PLEASE, MY KID...

14:46.469 --> 14:48.471
I'LL NEED
YOUR DRIVER'S LICENSE

14:48.471 --> 14:50.265
AND A SOCIAL SECURITY
NUMBER

14:50.265 --> 14:52.267
AND A MAJOR CREDIT CARD,

14:52.267 --> 14:54.144
AND A BIRTH CERTIFICATE,

14:54.144 --> 14:56.479
ENLISTMENT PAPERS,
IF YOU SERVED,

14:56.479 --> 14:58.815
ENLISTMENT PAPERS
IF YOU GOT DISCHARGED...

15:01.860 --> 15:04.529
NOW WATCH 'EM QUICK, PEEJ,
WE'RE RUNNING OUT OF TIME!

15:06.031 --> 15:07.615
(CHAINSAW REVVING)

15:07.615 --> 15:10.994
TOTAL SENSORY OVERLOAD!
WHAT A BLAST, HUH?

15:10.994 --> 15:12.370
(MUFFLED GROANS)

15:12.370 --> 15:15.540
UH-OH, THAT'S ALL THE GORE WE
GOT TIME FOR.

15:15.540 --> 15:19.669
ALL 12 MUTILATOR MOVIES?

15:19.669 --> 15:23.048
(SOBBING)
AND I ALWAYS CALLED HIM YELLOW!

15:23.048 --> 15:26.301
(SOBBING) FORGIVE ME!

15:26.301 --> 15:27.886
AW, TELL IT TO THE JUDGE!

15:29.471 --> 15:31.014
SON, SON!

15:34.559 --> 15:37.145
UH, MAX? MAYBE WE OUGHTA
TRY SOMETHING TAMER.

15:37.145 --> 15:39.856
LIKE, SKY-DIVING
OFF THE TRUMP TOWER!

15:42.400 --> 15:45.695
WHEN MY BEST BUDDY'S
LOOKIN' AT LIFE
IN PRISON WITH NO PAROLE,

15:45.695 --> 15:48.740
I'M NOT GONNA LET HIM MISS HIS
LAST CHANCE TO BREAK HIS NECK!

15:48.740 --> 15:53.036
PJ, WAIT FOR DADDY!

15:53.036 --> 15:55.121
(SCREAMING)

15:55.121 --> 15:57.374
(SCREAMS)

15:57.374 --> 15:59.918
MAX, YOU HEAR SOMETHING?

15:59.918 --> 16:03.213
IF I DIDN'T KNOW BETTER,
I'D SWEAR THAT SOUNDED LIKE DAD!

16:03.213 --> 16:05.256
NAH!

16:05.256 --> 16:06.466
(GASPING)

16:09.260 --> 16:12.931
KID'S TAKING THAT HILL
LIKE THERE'S NO TOMORROW!

16:12.931 --> 16:16.101
OH, SON! DON'T CUT
YOUR LIFE ANY SHORTER

16:16.101 --> 16:17.352
THAN IT ALREADY IS!

16:22.232 --> 16:23.233
(GASPING)

16:24.734 --> 16:26.569
PJ!

16:29.072 --> 16:31.449
(SIREN WAILING)

16:34.369 --> 16:35.954
YOU AGAIN?

16:35.954 --> 16:37.372
(BELL RINGING)

16:39.374 --> 16:40.625
(SCREAMING)

16:43.003 --> 16:44.004
MY BABY!

16:47.799 --> 16:49.384
MY BABY!

16:51.386 --> 16:53.388
SOME FUN, EH, PJ?

16:53.388 --> 16:55.306
CHECK IT OUT!

16:55.306 --> 16:57.267
CYNTHIA SNODFREW!

16:57.267 --> 16:59.728
WASN'T KISSING HER
ON YOUR LIST?

16:59.728 --> 17:00.770
(SMACK)

17:00.770 --> 17:01.771
EW!

17:03.606 --> 17:04.607
(COUGHING)

17:08.778 --> 17:11.573
OH, THE POOR KID!

17:11.573 --> 17:13.783
STARVED FOR AFFECTION!

17:13.783 --> 17:17.162
I NEVER SHOULDA STOPPED
KISSING HIM GOOD NIGHT!

17:18.705 --> 17:19.789
(TIRES SCREECHING)

17:19.789 --> 17:21.708
(SCREAMING)

17:25.378 --> 17:28.590
"HAVE YOU HUGGED YOUR KID
TODAY?"

17:30.008 --> 17:32.344
PJ!

17:32.344 --> 17:36.431
Man: WELCOME TO TERRORLAND,
THE SCARIEST RIDES ON EARTH!

17:36.431 --> 17:38.350
GUARANTEED TO RATTLE YOUR CAGE

17:38.350 --> 17:41.019
AND SPILL YOUR GUTS
OR YOUR MONEY BACK!

17:45.148 --> 17:46.816
THAT'S MY BOY!

17:46.816 --> 17:49.152
DOESN'T WANNA GO
SLOW AND PAINFUL,

17:49.152 --> 17:52.447
WANTS TO GO FAST AND PAINFUL!

17:52.447 --> 17:54.824
FIFTEEN MINUTES TILL YOUR DAD
GETS YOUR REPORT CARD!

17:54.824 --> 17:57.660
WE'VE STILL GOT THREE THRILL
RIDES AND 10 BURGERS TO GO!

17:57.660 --> 18:00.163
Pete: SON! SON!

18:00.163 --> 18:01.373
IT'S DAD!

18:01.373 --> 18:02.707
DON'T WORRY, I'LL STALL HIM!

18:12.717 --> 18:14.135
LET GO, I'VE GOT
TO TALK TO MY KID!

18:14.135 --> 18:17.514
NO, NO! YOU SEE,
HE'S CONTAGIOUS TILL 3:30!

18:17.514 --> 18:19.391
OH, ME? WELL,
I GOT ANTIBODIES.

18:19.391 --> 18:23.353
YOU, YOU GOT A FAMILY!
YOU CAN'T TAKE THE RISK!

18:23.353 --> 18:26.856
WHAT ARE YOU...
(STAMMERING) CONTAGIOUS?

18:26.856 --> 18:29.859
WELL, I GUESS
I CAN WAIT 14 MINUTES.

18:29.859 --> 18:33.530
MEANWHILE, SHOW HIM
A BANG-UP TIME ON HIS OLD MAN!

18:33.530 --> 18:35.073
(SCREAMING)

18:53.925 --> 18:55.427
NINE MINUTES AND COUNTING!

18:55.427 --> 18:58.346
Max: MAN, ARE YOU BRAVE!

18:58.346 --> 19:00.515
IT'S THE BARREL OF FUN!

19:00.515 --> 19:01.766
(MUMBLING)

19:01.766 --> 19:04.019
(SCREAMING)

19:04.019 --> 19:05.895
(MECHANICAL RATTLING)

19:18.283 --> 19:19.534
TWO MINUTES TO GO!

19:19.534 --> 19:21.453
SAVED THE BEST FOR LAST,

19:21.453 --> 19:23.371
THE HAMMER SLAMMER!

19:27.751 --> 19:30.837
PEEJ, BEFORE YOU'RE
GROUNDED FOREVER,

19:30.837 --> 19:32.839
I JUST WANT YOU TO KNOW...

19:32.839 --> 19:34.799
YOU'RE THE BEST BUD
I EVER HAD!

19:34.799 --> 19:38.136
I FEEL LIKE I'M LOSING
THE CHERRY ON MY SUNDAE.

19:38.136 --> 19:39.637
THE FOAM ON MY ROOT BEER.

19:39.637 --> 19:41.973
THE CRUD UNDER MY FINGERNAILS.

19:41.973 --> 19:44.559
GO AHEAD, MAX.
(HICCUPPING)

19:44.559 --> 19:45.727
DO IT.

19:46.811 --> 19:48.438
(SOBBING) WHAT A GUY.

19:51.232 --> 19:52.233
(CLANGING)

19:58.448 --> 20:00.825
I CAN'T LET HIM GET
POUNDED TO A PULP

20:00.825 --> 20:03.661
BEFORE HE HAS A CHANCE
TO FORGIVE ME!

20:03.661 --> 20:04.996
I GOTTA CHOOSE,

20:04.996 --> 20:08.792
KILLER GERMS
OR LIFELONG GUILT!

20:08.792 --> 20:12.170
JUMP, SON!
DADDY WILL SAVE YOU!

20:16.049 --> 20:19.135
ONE MINUTE 12 SECONDS!
GO! GO! GO!

20:21.680 --> 20:23.598
YES! WE DID IT!

20:29.604 --> 20:31.856
ERR... SON!

20:34.859 --> 20:36.194
I WANT YOU TO KNOW

20:36.194 --> 20:37.987
ALL THOSE NASTY HORRIBLE
THINGS I DID TO YOU

20:37.987 --> 20:39.823
WERE DONE WITH ONLY
THE BEST INTENTIONS,

20:39.823 --> 20:43.827
SO IF YOU COULD POSSIBLY FIND IT
IN YOUR HEART TO FORGIVE...

20:43.827 --> 20:45.036
(TELEPHONE RINGING)

20:45.036 --> 20:47.247
HANG ON, I'LL GET IT.

20:47.247 --> 20:49.416
HELLO? DR. HOWARD?

20:49.416 --> 20:52.460
I CAN'T TALK NOW,
MY KID ONLY HAS MINUTES TO LIVE!

20:52.460 --> 20:54.212
NO, HE DOESN'T.

20:54.212 --> 20:56.715
HE'S GOT A COMMON AILMENT
AMONG SCHOOL-AGED CHILDREN

20:56.715 --> 20:58.800
WITH TEST PERFORMANCE ANXIETY.

20:58.800 --> 21:01.261
IT'S CALLED FAKING.

21:01.261 --> 21:03.596
FAKING? WELL,
THAT WILL BE FINE.

21:04.806 --> 21:06.141
FAKING?

21:07.976 --> 21:11.062
DAD, I DON'T FEEL SO GOOD.

21:11.062 --> 21:13.356
WHY'D YOU CUT SCHOOL
OVER A STUPID TEST?

21:13.356 --> 21:16.651
WELL, 'CAUSE YOU SAID
IF I...FLUNKED,

21:16.651 --> 21:18.361
I'D BE GROUNDED FOR LIFE!

21:18.361 --> 21:20.405
WHAT? WHAT DO YOU MEAN,

21:20.405 --> 21:21.990
THINKING I'D REALLY
GROUND YOU FOR LIFE?

21:21.990 --> 21:23.825
I'D NEVER GROUND YOU FOR LIFE!

21:23.825 --> 21:25.201
HOW MANY TIMES
I GOTTA TELL YOU?

21:25.201 --> 21:28.246
DO AS I THINK,
NOT MEAN WHAT I SAY!

21:28.246 --> 21:30.290
JUST FOR THAT,
YOU'RE GROUNDED FOR LIFE!

21:32.459 --> 21:35.003
MILKSHAKE, I'M HOME!

21:35.003 --> 21:38.423
AND PJ'S REPORT CARD
CAME IN THE MAIL.

21:38.423 --> 21:42.802
NOW SEE THERE, SUGAR CONE?
HE GOT AN "A" IN MATH!

21:42.802 --> 21:45.680
AN "A"?

21:48.350 --> 21:53.605
YAHOO! MY KID WITH
MY BRAINS GOT MY "A"!

21:53.605 --> 21:57.734
SON, WE'RE GONNA CELEBRATE!

21:57.734 --> 21:59.778
I'M TREATIN' YOU
TO EVERYTHING YOU LIKE!

21:59.778 --> 22:02.405
TERRORLAND, MUTILATOR
MOVIES, THE WORKS!

22:02.405 --> 22:04.616
I'M BUYIN' YOU 200
GORILLA BURGERS!

22:04.616 --> 22:06.910
NO, NO, NO,
300 GORILLA BURGERS!

22:06.910 --> 22:09.412
AND THEN, WHEN YOU ACE YOUR
SCIENCE TEST NEXT WEEK,

22:09.412 --> 22:11.956
I'LL BUY YOU 600!

22:11.956 --> 22:13.833
(LAUGHS)

22:13.833 --> 22:15.710
AIN'T LIFE GRAND?
